Tue 4/27/2021 6:24 PM
  • Chandrasekharan, Rajesh (Contractor) <Rajesh.Chandrasekharan@rb.com>
  • Newman, Darlene <Darlene.Newman@rb.com>;
  • Lam, Albert <Albert.Lam@rb.com>

Hi Team

Thank you for joining the call, the meeting notes from the call are as follows,

 

1. Pop-up component issue

  • Ameex was advised to overwrite the pop-up component on react front end.
  • The current pop-up is controlled via cookies and this functionality cannot be directly used
  • Ameex team to work on this approach

2. Recaptcha set up

  • To set up Recaptcha Ameex need to enter the API key at Site configuration> Third party Integration> Google Recapcha settings
  • This can be generated by the Business team using the link, https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin/create
  • Market/ Business Unit needs to generate the key
  • The implemented captcha is an Invisible Recaptcha mechanism this does not require a front end interface to click and verify the user as a bot or a real user

3. CDS integration

  • PE ticket is created to add the forms component to the site to implement the CDS connectivity

4. Code review

  • In progress and Ameex has no major question on the same.

Regards

Justin
